><div style=3D"color:#000000;direction:ltr;font-family:&#39;Inter&#39;,&#39=
;Arial&#39;;font-size:17px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:1=
50%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"margin:0;margi=
n-bottom:0px;">As for whether the U.S. <em>should</em> reassess the actual =
malice standard
articulated in <em>Sullivan</em>, well=E2=80=A6 that=E2=80=99s a separate q=
uestion. Perhaps it=E2=80=99s surprising to read this from a journalist, bu=
t maybe Justice Gorsuch was onto something when he <a href=3D"https://email=
=2Epuck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVD=
J4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dWRzdoQ1FMb0JPaHhr=
Q0VqV3FGST0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubGF3LmNvcm5lbGwuZWR1L3N1cHJlbWVjb3V=
ydC90ZXh0LzIwLTEwNjM_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPVdoYXQrSSUyN20rSGVhcmluZyUyQistK1NVQl=
NDUklCRVJTKyUyODIlMkYxOCUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX2NvbnRlbnQ9V2hhdCtJJTI3bStIZ=
WFyaW5nJTJCKy0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MiUyRjE4JTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fbWVkaXVt=
